  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Shelter and Non-Food Items (ESNFI) assistance to populations affected by crises in Jara, North Wello, Amhara regions of Ethiopia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed intervention will provide lifesaving humanitarian assistance focusing on Shelter support targeting Internally Displaced People (IDPs) in Jara IDP Site, North Wello, Amhara region. Key activities will include construction of communal shelters and distribution of emergency shelters and Non-Food Item (NFI) kits. Through Implementing Partner, Development for Peace Organization (DPO), 3,820 households (17,190 individuals) will have access to safe and dignified shelter solutions.</narrative>
  </description>
